description:
Samantha Sin is back and takes on the 5th ranked Ariel X. Samantha has taken a liking to US and hopes to become a top ranked contender before the season is over.

Unfortunately for Samantha, she is completely schooled on the mat. The painful lesson she learned once before becomes fresh in her mind again, as her face is brutally slammed into the mat, is that there is nothing easy about wrestling at Ultimate Surrender. She thought wrestling the 5th ranked Ariel X would be a cake walk compared to Vendetta, never has someone been so wrong.
title: Ariel X "The Assassin" (5-2) vs Samantha Sin "The Python" (0-1)
